1
00:00:00,470 --> 00:00:08,570
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,745 --> 00:00:16,982
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,220 --> 00:00:19,211
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,225 --> 00:00:25,991
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,062 --> 00:00:29,429
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,632 --> 00:00:33,193
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,569 --> 00:00:36,936
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:37,006 --> 00:00:44,435
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,514 --> 00:00:53,650
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,723 --> 00:01:01,755
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:01,998 --> 00:01:08,836
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,905 --> 00:01:16,971
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:25,745
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,822 --> 00:01:27,847
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:30,871 --> 00:01:32,236
The winner is Temari.

16
00:01:52,859 --> 00:01:55,020
Oh, I'm tired...

17
00:02:00,067 --> 00:02:02,695
Oh, what a waste!

18
00:02:03,370 --> 00:02:07,101
Why?! He had a chance to
become a Chunin!

19
00:02:07,941 --> 00:02:09,704
Shikamaru is Shikamaru...

20
00:02:13,780 --> 00:02:17,375
Really... Does he or doesn't he
have the motivation?

21
00:02:17,718 --> 00:02:21,620
Even I'm not sure about it.

22
00:02:23,490 --> 00:02:27,950
<i>But his intelligence and strategies</i>
<i>are no longer at the Genin level.</i>

23
00:02:30,130 --> 00:02:34,123
<i>If it had been an actual mission</i>
<i>for a basic platoon,</i>

24
00:02:34,368 --> 00:02:38,464
<i>the win was decided when</i>
<i>he captured Temari...</i>

25
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:43,332
<i>So, I suppose he won the competition,</i>
<i>but he lost the match...</i>

26
00:02:45,312 --> 00:02:48,611
<i>It's unfortunate he shows no</i>
<i>signs of being motivated,</i>

27
00:02:50,017 --> 00:02:55,216
<i>on the other hand, he won't get too</i>
<i>emotional or fall into a panic.</i>

28
00:02:55,822 --> 00:02:56,914
<i>And that's exactly why...</i>

29
00:02:57,157 --> 00:03:01,389
<i>he'd be able to calmly pull back if</i>
<i>he viewed a situation as totally hopeless.</i>

30
00:03:02,396 --> 00:03:05,456
<i>That could be attributed to</i>
<i>calm judgment.</i>

31
00:03:06,099 --> 00:03:07,123
<i>Shikamaru probably possesses...</i>

32
00:03:07,968 --> 00:03:13,770
<i>the most important psychological</i>
<i>element required for a Chunin...</i>

33
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:16,240
<i>the disposition of a leader!</i>

34
00:03:25,852 --> 00:03:28,719
In order to evaluate someone
as a leader of a platoon...

35
00:03:28,822 --> 00:03:31,552
it's much more important to
protect the platoon from danger,

36
00:03:31,625 --> 00:03:35,459
than to carry out a mission.

37
00:03:35,829 --> 00:03:39,026
Yeah... it'd hardly be worth mentioning
a completed mission

38
00:03:39,099 --> 00:03:41,590
if everyone was annihilated.

39
00:03:42,102 --> 00:03:44,332
The risks and the mission
should be put on a scale,

40
00:03:44,404 --> 00:03:47,771
surviving should be thought of first,
and then action should be taken.

41
00:03:47,874 --> 00:03:49,899
A person who can't do this isn't
qualified to become a Chunin.

42
00:03:50,510 --> 00:03:54,276
Hyuga and Naruto from earlier
fail on that point.

43
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:03,086
Although they are all right
as insignificant Genin.

44
00:04:04,357 --> 00:04:08,054
Well, I do feel like Shikamaru
gave up too soon too.

45
00:04:11,765 --> 00:04:12,663
What do you think?

46
00:04:14,167 --> 00:04:15,600
What do I feel...?

47
00:04:17,270 --> 00:04:19,966
He has more of a chance
than Naruto, for sure!

48
00:04:20,373 --> 00:04:21,032
Shoot...!

49
00:04:24,778 --> 00:04:28,214
Why the heck did he give up!

50
00:04:29,149 --> 00:04:30,582
Is he an idiot?!

51
00:04:30,984 --> 00:04:32,576
This ticks me off!

52
00:04:33,887 --> 00:04:36,685
I'm gonna really give him
a lecture!

53
00:04:37,557 --> 00:04:40,321
So the one that's gonna
become a Chunin is...

54
00:04:41,895 --> 00:04:43,123
You idiot!

55
00:04:43,797 --> 00:04:45,424
Shut up, super idiot!

56
00:04:45,632 --> 00:04:49,398
Why the heck did you give up?!

57
00:04:49,636 --> 00:04:52,833
Let's not talk about that anymore,
all right?

58
00:04:53,473 --> 00:04:56,909
It's not all right! It was a match
you were close to winning!

59
00:04:56,977 --> 00:05:00,879
- Let's just watch the next match.
- But you just gave up! Unimaginable!

60
00:05:00,947 --> 00:05:02,812
Simply unimaginable!

61
00:05:03,350 --> 00:05:04,874
Huh? The next match?

62
00:05:11,858 --> 00:05:12,790
Sasuke...!

63
00:05:13,693 --> 00:05:19,598
<i>"Dancing Leaf, Squirming Sand"</i>

64
00:05:21,735 --> 00:05:23,669
At last, Uchiha's match is next.

65
00:05:24,037 --> 00:05:27,131
Oh, but who's this opponent Gaara?

66
00:05:27,407 --> 00:05:28,066
I wonder...

67
00:05:28,341 --> 00:05:31,242
But compared to Uchiha,
he's nothing much.

68
00:05:34,147 --> 00:05:35,079
Do you know?

69
00:05:35,382 --> 00:05:38,112
I hear Uchiha's gonna
withdraw from this match.

70
00:05:38,218 --> 00:05:39,412
Really?!

71
00:05:39,686 --> 00:05:43,178
Yeah, he apparently sustained a serious
injury while training before the match...

72
00:05:43,323 --> 00:05:44,950
Are you serious?

73
00:05:45,358 --> 00:05:49,021
And to think I took time off
specifically to see this match!

74
00:05:49,696 --> 00:05:51,357
I'm counting on you, come on!

75
00:05:53,066 --> 00:05:56,433
As you'd expect, this match
will be won by Uchiha.

76
00:05:57,270 --> 00:06:01,434
No way, I've got high hope
for the new one of the Sand.

77
00:06:01,708 --> 00:06:04,142
He won't let this one slip by.

78
00:06:06,213 --> 00:06:09,011
As they say about the world
of competition...

79
00:06:09,749 --> 00:06:13,742
It's impossible to predict
what will occur...

80
00:06:48,588 --> 00:06:51,819
Lord Hokage, about Uchiha Sasuke,

81
00:06:52,058 --> 00:06:54,219
he has not yet arrived at the arena.

82
00:06:55,328 --> 00:06:57,990
Umm... it's unavoidable...

83
00:06:59,165 --> 00:07:02,532
We can't make the guests
wait any longer.

84
00:07:03,303 --> 00:07:04,429
Another ten minutes.

85
00:07:06,039 --> 00:07:08,667
Why don't we wait just
another ten minutes?

86
00:07:09,175 --> 00:07:09,834
But...

87
00:07:10,377 --> 00:07:14,336
The guests are looking forward
to the next match above all else.

88
00:07:15,482 --> 00:07:17,780
Cancelling it would be cruel.

89
00:07:18,585 --> 00:07:22,316
Since it's come to this,
waiting another ten minutes wouldn't hurt.

90
00:07:25,158 --> 00:07:26,182
Lord Hokage...?

91
00:07:26,793 --> 00:07:27,555
Umm...

92
00:07:28,094 --> 00:07:29,994
Uchiha, where are you!

93
00:07:30,063 --> 00:07:31,724
What's keeping you?
Hurry up!

94
00:07:33,633 --> 00:07:37,228
There is some truth to what
Kazekage says.

95
00:07:37,837 --> 00:07:42,934
So shall we extend it for
ten minutes from now.

96
00:07:48,315 --> 00:07:50,977
So... let Genma know of this.

97
00:07:52,052 --> 00:07:52,643
Yes!

98
00:07:59,559 --> 00:08:02,687
<i>If it stays like this, Uchiha will really</i>
<i>be forced to withdraw.</i>

99
00:08:07,167 --> 00:08:10,261
<i>I see...a ten minute extension...</i>

100
00:08:16,042 --> 00:08:16,940
<i>Sasuke...</i>

101
00:08:23,516 --> 00:08:25,108
Hey, isn't that...

102
00:08:38,832 --> 00:08:40,959
Y-You are...

103
00:08:44,371 --> 00:08:48,603
But, what's that idiot doing
He's still not here?!

104
00:08:52,912 --> 00:08:53,936
<i>Sasuke...!</i>

105
00:08:55,382 --> 00:08:56,144
<i>Please!</i>

106
00:08:58,451 --> 00:09:00,351
Good of the two of you to make it!

107
00:09:00,653 --> 00:09:02,621
Come now, hurry into the arena!

108
00:09:06,326 --> 00:09:06,883
Yeah!

109
00:09:09,229 --> 00:09:10,753
All right! Here we go!

110
00:09:10,930 --> 00:09:11,988
Oh! Yeah!

111
00:09:12,899 --> 00:09:15,129
Most of the first round is finished,

112
00:09:15,268 --> 00:09:18,294
and the only one left is
Sasuke Uchiha and Gaara.

113
00:09:21,741 --> 00:09:23,538
H-How about Naruto and
Neji's match?!

114
00:09:24,244 --> 00:09:26,178
Well, the interesting thing is...

115
00:09:29,015 --> 00:09:30,846
That Hyuga lost...

116
00:09:38,758 --> 00:09:41,556
<i>Naruto beat Neji...</i>

117
00:09:49,836 --> 00:09:50,734
I see...

118
00:09:56,443 --> 00:09:57,307
<i>You did it!</i>

119
00:09:58,878 --> 00:09:59,776
<i>Naruto!</i>

120
00:10:01,014 --> 00:10:03,847
<i>You're such a...</i>
<i>good guy really...</i>

121
00:10:05,018 --> 00:10:07,248
- What's going on with the next match!
- Let's get on with it!

122
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,981
Isn't Uchiha up yet?!

123
00:10:09,122 --> 00:10:11,056
We want Uchiha! Uchiha!

124
00:10:11,191 --> 00:10:12,453
Uchiha!

125
00:10:14,794 --> 00:10:16,489
Hey, it's almost time.

126
00:10:17,263 --> 00:10:18,821
Is he really gonna come?!

127
00:10:20,066 --> 00:10:20,896
He'll come...

128
00:10:26,439 --> 00:10:27,872
He'll definitely come!

129
00:10:33,346 --> 00:10:37,578
Oh Sasuke, what's he doing!

130
00:10:37,917 --> 00:10:41,045
What the heck is Uchiha doing?!

131
00:10:43,323 --> 00:10:47,555
It seems the rumor that
he'd had a serious injury was true.

132
00:10:47,961 --> 00:10:51,362
If there's a win by default,
then this match is mine.

133
00:10:55,235 --> 00:10:56,862
<i>Thirty more seconds...</i>

134
00:10:57,704 --> 00:10:58,329
Uchiha!

135
00:11:01,407 --> 00:11:02,601
Uchiha!

136
00:11:09,048 --> 00:11:11,448
<i>Sasuke...please come!</i>

137
00:11:11,784 --> 00:11:12,682
Sasuke!

138
00:11:13,453 --> 00:11:15,182
Hurry up and come!

139
00:11:15,388 --> 00:11:17,788
It won't be good if it stays this way!

140
00:11:18,992 --> 00:11:20,755
<i>The time limit is up.</i>

141
00:11:22,128 --> 00:11:23,390
<i>So this is it.</i>

142
00:11:24,264 --> 00:11:28,894
Because the time limit has expired,
the last match...

143
00:12:10,009 --> 00:12:12,034
See... Here he is...

144
00:12:13,212 --> 00:12:16,147
Well, I'm sorry we're late...

145
00:12:19,385 --> 00:12:20,317
Sasu...

146
00:12:22,989 --> 00:12:23,785
Your name?

147
00:12:27,627 --> 00:12:30,027
Sasuke... Uchiha.

148
00:12:35,568 --> 00:12:37,968
Sasuke... Uchiha.

149
00:12:39,572 --> 00:12:40,539
Sasuke!

150
00:12:42,575 --> 00:12:43,735
It looks like he made it in time.

151
00:12:44,977 --> 00:12:45,671
Lee!

152
00:12:49,115 --> 00:12:52,676
<i>Darn... Causing others</i>
<i>this much trouble...</i>

153
00:12:52,752 --> 00:12:53,741
<i>and thinking himself so important!</i>

154
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:57,616
Huh! You're pretty late!

155
00:12:57,923 --> 00:13:01,484
I thought you weren't coming
'cause you were scared to take me on!

156
00:13:01,694 --> 00:13:04,629
<i>Who the heck was it that</i>
<i>said he'd come for sure?</i>

157
00:13:05,564 --> 00:13:08,192
The first round... did you win?

158
00:13:08,601 --> 00:13:09,568
Of course!

159
00:13:11,303 --> 00:13:13,066
Don't get too carried away...

160
00:13:13,539 --> 00:13:14,631
Loser!

161
00:13:21,347 --> 00:13:26,080
Well, I know it's somewhat rude
to be showing up all flashy like this...

162
00:13:27,053 --> 00:13:28,850
but was Sasuke...

163
00:13:29,889 --> 00:13:30,981
disqualified?

164
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:38,753
So your habit of tardiness
rubbed off on him? Cripes...

165
00:13:39,432 --> 00:13:41,059
And... what about it?

166
00:13:41,867 --> 00:13:46,964
It's all right, Sasuke's match
has been postponed anyway.

167
00:13:47,573 --> 00:13:49,666
Your arrival was barely in time, but...

168
00:13:50,376 --> 00:13:51,900
he hasn't been disqualified.

169
00:13:53,212 --> 00:13:55,510
That's good to hear!

170
00:14:06,425 --> 00:14:08,450
Don't lose to a guy like that!

171
00:14:09,428 --> 00:14:10,019
Yeah...

172
00:14:15,101 --> 00:14:17,831
<i>I want to fight you too...</i>

173
00:14:18,704 --> 00:14:19,534
Sasuke!

174
00:14:23,776 --> 00:14:27,735
I want... to fight you too!

175
00:14:33,185 --> 00:14:33,708
Yeah...

176
00:14:37,189 --> 00:14:39,623
Yay, Sasuke!

177
00:14:39,925 --> 00:14:41,222
Uchiha's match is gonna start!

178
00:14:41,293 --> 00:14:44,023
<i>Shikamaru gave it so much,</i>
<i>but already it's Sasuke...</i>

179
00:14:44,296 --> 00:14:46,093
<i>Poor Shikamaru...</i>

180
00:14:46,999 --> 00:14:48,364
Hey, is that Uchiha?

181
00:14:49,001 --> 00:14:51,435
<i>I'm just second fiddle...</i>

182
00:14:52,538 --> 00:14:54,369
<i>Well, I guess that's just</i>
<i>the way it goes...</i>

183
00:14:55,374 --> 00:14:57,137
<i>I'm looking forward to it too.</i>

184
00:14:58,944 --> 00:15:01,970
Your team is sort of amazing, Sakura.

185
00:15:02,515 --> 00:15:03,345
What is?

186
00:15:03,549 --> 00:15:07,781
Well, Naruto did beat that
Neji Hyuga and...

187
00:15:08,387 --> 00:15:10,446
Sasuke is an elite member
of the Uchiha...

188
00:15:10,689 --> 00:15:15,251
and it seems like everyone's
anxious to see Sasuke's match.

189
00:15:19,765 --> 00:15:24,259
<i>Sasuke will face that Gaara</i>
<i>of the Sand whom I couldn't beat...</i>

190
00:15:25,137 --> 00:15:29,904
<i>And Naruto beat that Neji</i>
<i>that I had hoped to take down.</i>

191
00:15:38,951 --> 00:15:39,975
<i>Why is it so...</i>

192
00:15:43,989 --> 00:15:45,479
<i>Why am I so...</i>

193
00:15:51,530 --> 00:15:52,724
<i>frustrated!</i>

194
00:15:55,134 --> 00:15:55,930
<i>Lee...!</i>

195
00:16:07,913 --> 00:16:08,971
<i>At last...</i>

196
00:16:24,396 --> 00:16:26,387
Gaara, come down here!

197
00:16:27,266 --> 00:16:29,131
Naruto! Let's go up!

198
00:16:29,702 --> 00:16:30,430
Yeah!

199
00:16:33,739 --> 00:16:36,572
When we go up,
we'll leisurely take the stairs.

200
00:16:36,709 --> 00:16:38,040
What's up with you!

201
00:16:38,110 --> 00:16:40,374
Are you still upset that
I pushed you down?!

202
00:16:48,387 --> 00:16:49,285
<i>T-This isn't good...</i>

203
00:16:50,322 --> 00:16:52,187
<i>It's been quite awhile</i>
<i>since I've seen Gaara like this.</i>

204
00:16:52,725 --> 00:16:54,716
H-Hey... Gaara.

205
00:16:55,327 --> 00:16:56,885
Keep the strategy in mind...!

206
00:17:04,770 --> 00:17:06,533
Don't talk to Gaara right now!

207
00:17:09,541 --> 00:17:10,508
You'll be killed.

208
00:17:17,616 --> 00:17:18,105
Right!

209
00:17:19,285 --> 00:17:20,274
Let's go

210
00:17:25,457 --> 00:17:27,288
Hey, hurry up!

211
00:17:27,860 --> 00:17:30,556
Nothing good's gonna happen
in your life if you panic.

212
00:17:32,865 --> 00:17:33,559
What's wrong?

213
00:17:35,167 --> 00:17:35,792
Huh?

214
00:17:50,249 --> 00:17:54,345
Low level tournaments like this
Chunin Examination are ideal

215
00:17:54,420 --> 00:17:56,752
as gambling matches.

216
00:17:57,289 --> 00:18:00,725
A number of feudal lords
are here for that purpose.

217
00:18:01,327 --> 00:18:04,990
So... would you lose this match for us.

218
00:18:14,673 --> 00:18:17,540
Hey, come on,
at least give us an answer.

219
00:18:22,247 --> 00:18:23,942
Too scared to say anything...

220
00:19:05,023 --> 00:19:06,388
H-Help!

221
00:19:09,094 --> 00:19:11,028
S-Stop! Stop!

222
00:20:36,982 --> 00:20:39,075
If those two in front of us
hadn't been there,

223
00:20:39,685 --> 00:20:41,550
we probably would've been killed...

224
00:20:42,654 --> 00:20:46,590
This is the first I've seen anyone
kill people without hesitation like that...

225
00:20:47,593 --> 00:20:49,527
This isn't looking good
even for Sasuke.

226
00:20:51,396 --> 00:20:52,260
<i>Sasuke...</i>

227
00:21:02,107 --> 00:21:04,075
So now... at last...

228
00:21:07,813 --> 00:21:17,882
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

229
00:21:18,324 --> 00:21:29,167
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

230
00:21:39,278 --> 00:21:44,910
<i>Yes, breathe in the air</i>
<i>Lift your face to the sky and jump</i>

231
00:21:44,984 --> 00:21:49,944
<i>If it rains, take a break</i>
<i>Go where the wind takes you</i>

232
00:21:50,322 --> 00:21:55,225
<i>So many regrets</i>
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>

233
00:21:55,427 --> 00:21:58,624
<i>Let's go carve the badges</i>
<i>in our chest</i>

234
00:21:58,697 --> 00:22:00,426
<i>Yes, it's Show Time,</i>
<i>life begins now.</i>

235
00:22:00,499 --> 00:22:10,670
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

236
00:22:10,976 --> 00:22:21,409
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

237
00:22:21,487 --> 00:22:32,056
<i>Transform sadness into the wind</i>
<i>and continue to forge on</i>

238
00:22:32,131 --> 00:22:37,694
<i>Forge on strong</i>

239
00:22:49,649 --> 00:22:51,810
Darn it!
What kind of guy is that?!

240
00:22:51,885 --> 00:22:56,913
Gaara is totally not normal!
He doesn't even look at us.

241
00:22:57,324 --> 00:22:59,121
If anyone fights with him like that...

242
00:22:59,526 --> 00:23:02,427
Darn! Hey Shikamaru!
We've got to go see Kakashi Sensei!

243
00:23:02,762 --> 00:23:05,128
We've got to stop this fight,
no matter what!

244
00:23:06,066 --> 00:23:10,127
Next time, "Bushy Brow's Jutsu:
Sasuke Style!"

245
00:23:10,537 --> 00:23:13,665
If nothing's done,
Sasuke's a goner!
